snippet.title: Leak Project
snippet.description:
The Leak Project was created to offer awareness and information not found in the main stream news.  
With over 90% of the Worlds Media controlled by only 6 Enormous Conglomerates, 
many people are looking for more accurate information.  
The Leak Project offers a refreshing approach to the brain drain media. 
Live Shows, Check back daily for new content as we thrive to bring you the cutting edge in news, current events, on scene video footage, interviews and information.
http://www.leakproject.com
